text: Jit is a 1990 Zimbabwean romantic comedy movie directed by Michael Raeburn and starring Dominic Makuwachuma, Sibongile Nene, Farai Sevenzo, Winnie Ndemera, Oliver Mtukudzi, Lawrence Simbarashe. == Other websites == * Category:1990 romantic comedy movies Category:Zimbabwean movies Category:Movies directed by Michael Raeburn
